nodes.text: In 32 BBY, a Draag supervisor worked in the hangar of Haugg Nerf Industries in the industrial district of the planet Coruscant. One day, when a speeder that belonged to a Human death stick dealer named Jervis Gloom arrived without Gloom on it, the Draag suspected something unusual had happened. The reptilian told a Guineo lackey to guard the speeder, and the Draag left to inform the factory's boss, Groff Haugg. Before the Draag could do so, however, the bounty hunter Jango Fett intervened.
